We offer design-led solution for end to end execution of interior design. All on one platform.
 Our project management team has worked with over 3500 clients across Asia and Middle East.
 We respect the spirit of design while we empower our interior partners with the science behind it.

5000+ happy customers
They’ve loved us and so will you!

35 working days after the receipt of
payment. If there are any delays due to the
non-readiness of client’s site then the
schedule will shift accordingly.

10% advance on confirmation of booking,
balance payment on the finalisation of
design and quotations

5 years on manufacturing defect, from the
date of completion

● 100% cost shall be borne by our lease
partner “OPC Leasing Solutions”
● 12 quarters lease at the rate of Rs. 91.75
per 1000 per quarter (exclusive of GST)
● 10% deposit, 0.5% lease management fee
● Renewal Lease or Terminal Value after 12
quarters as per standard terms

1.Initial Design and Quotation Submission
2. Acceptance 3. Initial Payment 4. Final
Design and Quotation Submission 5. Final
Payment 6. Factory manufacturing 7. Final
installation and service coordination.
